{"tid":1761304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大鑊！民意逆轉咗好多人支持唔回應五大訴求！","createTime":"2019-11-28T23:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T00:18:00.000Z","uid":2415,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"17711a3280ad93a63fd0f9305ae52b3e5437f312","tid":1761304,"uid":2415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T23:13:11.000Z","msg":"點解？因為你哋成日<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打錯字</span></span>呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係五大訴求，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">缺</span></span>一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係五大訴求，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">決</span></span>一不可呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n錯其他字都話蒜狗掃，<br />\n呢粒字一錯成個意思掉轉晒呀！<br />\n<br />\n討論錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行動post都錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n貼堂傷感情<br />\n應承我，今日開始留意番好冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋識得笑殘體字求其<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識得笑黑狗唔讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對自己都要有要求先得㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ba8786213a81b5a9a3b257f1a6c097a1320db2","tid":1761304,"uid":188176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"rep